<para id="element-67">
<exercise id="exercise-67">
<problem id="id1172398476690">

<para id="element-69">A cubical block of mass “M” and sides “L” hits a small obstruction at "p", while moving with a velocity “v” as shown in the figure. If the the block topples, then the angular speed of the block about "P", just after it hits the obstruction, is :
</para>
<para id="element-70">
