<media id="id1172393519799" alt=""><image src="../../media/caq3.gif" mime-type="image/gif"/></media>
<caption> The cubical block moves with a velocity “v” on a horizontal surface.</caption>
</figure>
</para>
<para id="element-71">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>

<m:mi> (a) </m:mi>
<m:mspace width="4pt"/>
<m:mfrac>
