<m:mi> v </m:mi>
<m:mi> L </m:mi>
</m:mrow>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:mfrac>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math></para>
<para id="element-76">Negative sign indicates that the angular momentum of the block about "P" is clockwise. The angular momentum of the block after collision, now treating it as a rigid body rotating about the axis perpendicular to the plane of motion and passing through the point of obstruction, is :
</para>
<para id="element-77">
<figure id="fig-77">
<title> A block hitting an obstruction </title>
<media id="id4466264" alt=""><image src="../../media/caq4.gif" mime-type="image/gif"/></media>
