<m:mi> L </m:mi>
</m:mrow>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:mfrac>
<m:mo> = </m:mo> 
<m:mi> I </m:mi>
<m:mi> ω </m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-82">For moment of inertia of the block, it can be treated like a square plate. Its MI about the axis passing through COM is,
</para>
<para id="element-83">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
